    "Which pattern can suggest a cat needs more appropriate enrichment?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quel comportement peut suggérer qu’un chat a besoin d’un enrichissement plus adapté ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Restlessness or misdirected hunting can improve when the cat gets predictable play, exploration, and choice." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
