            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Utiliser une seule grande gamelle commune"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Remove the slower cat's meal" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Retirer le repas du chat le plus lent"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How should most routine food changes be introduced?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Comment introduire la plupart des changements alimentaires courants ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A gradual transition is often easier on digestion and gives you time to notice whether the new food suits the cat." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une transition progressive est souvent plus facile à digérer et laisse le temps de vérifier si le nouvel aliment convient au chat."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "All at once at a stressful time" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tout changer d’un coup pendant une période stressante"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Gradually while watching appetite and digestion" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Progressivement, en surveillant l’appétit et la digestion"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "By withholding water" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En supprimant l’eau"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "By mixing in unlimited treats" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "En ajoutant des friandises sans limite"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Why should treats remain a small part of a cat's overall diet?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pourquoi les friandises doivent-elles rester une petite part de l’alimentation globale du chat ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Too many extras can unbalance the diet or add unnoticed calories, even when each treat is small." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Trop d’extras peuvent déséquilibrer l’alimentation ou ajouter des calories inaperçues, même si chaque friandise est petite."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cats stop tasting them" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les chats finissent par ne plus les goûter"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Treats contain too much water" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les friandises contiennent trop d’eau"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "They can displace nutritionally complete food" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Elles peuvent remplacer une partie de l’alimentation nutritionnellement complète"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "They prevent all training" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Elles empêchent tout apprentissage"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A cat repeatedly pulls food out of a deep bowl. What simple change is worth trying?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un chat sort régulièrement la nourriture d’une gamelle profonde. Quel changement simple mérite d’être essayé ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Some cats are more comfortable eating from a stable, wide dish that does not crowd the face and whiskers." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Certains chats mangent plus confortablement dans une assiette stable et large qui ne gêne pas le visage ni les moustaches."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A taller narrow cup" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un récipient plus haut et étroit"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A moving bowl" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une gamelle mobile"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A bowl beside the litter box" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une gamelle à côté de la litière"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A wide, shallow dish" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une assiette large et peu profonde"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Which statement about wet and dry cat food is most useful?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quelle affirmation sur les aliments humides et secs est la plus utile ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The right choice depends on nutritional completeness, the individual cat, hydration, health needs, and veterinary guidance." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le bon choix dépend de l’équilibre nutritionnel, du chat, de son hydratation, de ses besoins de santé et des conseils vétérinaires."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Either can fit when the overall diet is complete and appropriate for the cat" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les deux peuvent convenir si l’alimentation globale est complète et adaptée au chat"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dry food never contains nutrients" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les aliments secs ne contiennent jamais de nutriments"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Wet food suits every medical condition" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les aliments humides conviennent à toutes les maladies"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The most expensive option is always best" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L’option la plus chère est toujours la meilleure"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "What should you do with moist food left sitting out for a long time?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Que faire d’un aliment humide resté longtemps à température ambiante ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Fresh portions and clean dishes reduce spoilage and make changes in appetite easier to measure." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Des portions fraîches et des récipients propres limitent l’altération et facilitent la mesure des changements d’appétit."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Top it up indefinitely" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le compléter indéfiniment"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Discard it and serve a fresh portion" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le jeter et servir une portion fraîche"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Mix it into the water bowl" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le mélanger à la gamelle d’eau"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Leave it until the next day" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le laisser jusqu’au lendemain"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Which common cooking ingredients should not be offered to cats?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quels ingrédients courants en cuisine ne doivent pas être proposés aux chats ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Onion, garlic, and related plants can be toxic to cats, including in powders and seasoned foods." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L’oignon, l’ail et les plantes apparentées peuvent être toxiques pour les chats, y compris sous forme de poudre ou dans des plats assaisonnés."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Plain cooked pumpkin" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De la courge cuite nature"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unseasoned cooked meat" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De la viande cuite non assaisonnée"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Onion and garlic" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De l’oignon et de l’ail"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A veterinary diet" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une alimentation vétérinaire"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Why is a bowl of cow's milk usually a poor everyday treat for an adult cat?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pourquoi un bol de lait de vache est-il généralement une mauvaise friandise quotidienne pour un chat adulte ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Many adult cats digest lactose poorly, so milk can cause stomach or bowel upset." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De nombreux chats adultes digèrent mal le lactose ; le lait peut donc provoquer des troubles digestifs."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It always causes allergies" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il provoque toujours des allergies"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It removes vitamins" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il élimine les vitamines"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It makes water unsafe" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il rend l’eau dangereuse"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Many adult cats do not tolerate lactose well" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De nombreux chats adultes tolèrent mal le lactose"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How should you introduce a food puzzle to a cat who has never used one?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Comment présenter un puzzle alimentaire à un chat qui n’en a jamais utilisé ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An easy first success builds confidence. Difficulty can increase after the cat understands how food is released." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une première réussite facile donne confiance. La difficulté peut augmenter une fois que le chat comprend comment libérer la nourriture."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Start easy and make it harder gradually" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Commencer facilement puis augmenter progressivement la difficulté"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hide every meal immediately" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cacher immédiatement tous les repas"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use it only when the cat is very hungry" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "L’utiliser seulement lorsque le chat a très faim"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Shake it loudly near the cat" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Le secouer bruyamment près du chat"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Which breathing sign needs urgent veterinary attention?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quel signe respiratoire nécessite des soins vétérinaires urgents ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open-mouth or labored breathing in a cat can be an emergency. Minimize stress and seek urgent veterinary help." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une respiration bouche ouverte ou laborieuse peut être une urgence chez le chat. Limitez le stress et consultez rapidement un vétérinaire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A quiet sigh before sleep" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un soupir discret avant de dormir"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open-mouth or visibly labored breathing" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une respiration bouche ouverte ou visiblement laborieuse"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sniffing a new blanket" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Renifler une nouvelle couverture"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purring during a greeting" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ronronner pendant une salutation"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Why can a sudden change in grooming matter?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pourquoi un changement soudain de toilettage peut-il être important ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Both reduced grooming and excessive grooming can be meaningful changes when compared with the cat's usual pattern." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une diminution comme un excès de toilettage peuvent être significatifs par rapport aux habitudes du chat."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It proves the cat dislikes water" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cela prouve que le chat n’aime pas l’eau"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It only reflects the season" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cela reflète uniquement la saison"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pain, illness, stress, or mobility changes can affect grooming" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La douleur, la maladie, le stress ou une mobilité réduite peuvent affecter le toilettage"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It means the coat is fully clean" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cela signifie que le pelage est parfaitement propre"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When is vomiting more concerning than an isolated mild episode?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quand des vomissements sont-ils plus inquiétants qu’un épisode léger et isolé ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Repeated vomiting or vomiting with other changes deserves prompt veterinary advice." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Des vomissements répétés ou accompagnés d’autres changements nécessitent rapidement un avis vétérinaire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When it happens near a rug" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lorsqu’ils surviennent près d’un tapis"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When the cat looks embarrassed" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lorsque le chat semble gêné"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When food is a new color" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lorsque la nourriture a une nouvelle couleur"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When it repeats or comes with lethargy, pain, or appetite loss" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lorsqu’ils se répètent ou s’accompagnent d’abattement, de douleur ou d’une perte d’appétit"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "An older cat is eating well but steadily losing weight. What should you do?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Un chat âgé mange bien mais perd régulièrement du poids. Que devez-vous faire ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unexplained weight loss is not a normal change to ignore, even when appetite appears strong." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Une perte de poids inexpliquée n’est pas un changement normal à ignorer, même si l’appétit semble bon."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Arrange a veterinary assessment" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Organiser un bilan vétérinaire"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Simply double every meal" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Doubler simplement chaque repas"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Assume it is normal aging" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Supposer qu’il s’agit du vieillissement normal"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Stop tracking the change" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cesser de suivre le changement"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Which cluster can point to mouth or dental discomfort?" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quel ensemble de signes peut indiquer une gêne buccale ou dentaire ?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Changes in chewing, food handling, breath, or mouth sensitivity can justify a veterinary dental check." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Des changements de mastication, de prise des aliments, d’haleine ou de sensibilité de la bouche peuvent justifier un contrôle dentaire vétérinaire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sleeping in sunlight" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dormir au soleil"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dropping food, bad breath, or chewing on one side" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
